name: ChillWithNAI
description:
This is a mix with Chillout and NAI, and makes the chillout mix accept some specific loras (that are persumably trained on NAI). This is highly experimental. Expect some updates in the next week, prehaps, as I play a bit more with merge block weights.

This model does not work that well with highres fix, unfortuneately. If you are getting incorrect anatomy consider using small upscale ratios (<1.5x upscaling). 2x upscaling produces usually 2x body parts.
